parameter-set DigisToClusters.txt:
----------------------------------

download input ROOT file

http://home.fnal.gov/~gutsche/software/new_edm/DigisToDigis-<release>.root

and rename it to

DigisToDigis.root

and use the parameter-set DigisToClusters.txt with cmsRun to cluster Digis

parameter-set ClustersTo1DLocal.txt:
------------------------------------

use parameter-set DigisToClusters.txt or download input ROOT file 

http://home.fnal.gov/~gutsche/software/new_edm/DigisToClusters-<release>.root

and rename it to

DigisToClusters.root

and use the parameter-set ClustersTo1DLocal.txt to convert Clusters into 1D local measurements

parameter-set DigisTo1DLocal.txt:
---------------------------------

download input ROOT file

http://home.fnal.gov/~gutsche/software/new_edm/DigisToDigis-<release>.root

and rename it to

DigisToDigis.root

and use the parameter-set DigisTo11DLocal.txt with cmsRun to cluster Digis and convert Clusters into 1D local measurements
